snippet.title: Johnny Depp Showed His Severed Finger photos VS The Sun and Amber Heard
snippet.description:
In this video, we’re going to talk about Johnny Depp's Finger Photos Shown in Court VS the Sun and Amber Heard. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

Hollywood star Johnny Depp wrote on a wall with blood from his severed fingertip during a long and vioIent confrontation with his ex-wife Amber Heard, London's High Court heard on last Thursday ( 9th July ) at his libel case against a British tabloid.

Johnny Depp told the court he suffered "some species of nervous breakdown" during a row with actress Heard, but denied he had violently attacked her and accused her of cutting his finger by throwing a bottle at him.
